Whisk eggs with milk in a large bowl. Add self-raising flour to the mixture, then add mixed vegetables, bacon and herbs.
Mix ingredients until combined and pour into prepared lined and greased pan.
Bake for 30-35 minutes until golden and firm.
Cool in pan. Cut into slices and serve with salad.
